		<title>#wpvinnova: Einladung zum BIZZTALK SS2012</title>
		<link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/EnterpriseMeetsFuture/~3/p5dWyJLVY4o/</link>
		<comments>http://www.illik-online.com/wordpress_blogpod/?p=2776#comments</comments>
